{"tid":657504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【動漫電玩節】7月27日開鑼 首度推電競活動","createTime":"2018-05-08T07:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:57:28.000Z","uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9898ae7e7ceecc5105917dcae282f5343e7d2218","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"第20屆動漫電玩節（ACGHK 2018）將於7月27日起，一連五日在會議展覽中心舉行。大會更首度舉行「電競嘉年華」，有多間電競參展商舉辦不同活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/152249_717c438f0277fb3bdc1b574012cf1f92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F152249_717c438f0277fb3bdc1b574012cf1f92.png&h=0aeebbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年一度的香港動漫電玩節將於7月27日開鑼。（歐嘉樂攝）<br />\n<br />\n動漫迷期待的動漫節，將於7月27日至7月31日於會展一號及三號展覽廳舉行，並首度舉行「電競嘉年華」，有PlayStation、CSL Mobile Limited等多間參展商舉辦各種電競活動。<br />\n<br />\n此外，大會又與電競賽事專家Nova eSports LImited舉辦「ACGHK x Nova手遊電競亞洲群英賽」，包括兩項地區性大型比賽，「《爐石戰記》港台冠軍邀請賽」及「SUPERCELL《皇室戰爭》官方比賽」，前者邀請港台4位名人選手出賽，於7月29日至31日進行「對戰」，賽事總獎金為1萬元美金（約7.8萬港元）；後者則有中國、韓國、日本及東南亞的4個隊伍參賽，賽事總獎金為2萬元美金（約15.7萬港元）。"},{"pid":"461ba53e841e075910c4cdcc367bd8f7595a82e4","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f072accfc9bebd811f79acb34ee47c866968f3a","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8953abb95d98f6421854e541bada4a120ea786","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afccaa547605ae713784759cd95762f47e68307","tid":657504,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"300蚊Q 既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d201e61c4dc598895881b415843491da06b27d9b","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"手機電莖一啲都唔吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd73890323029505ce53055992789b03a23296f","tid":657504,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}